      "text": "👥 sales-ops\n  prospect research + lead enrichment\n\n🎧 support\n  ticket triage + escalation drafts\n\n💰 finance\n  month-end close + anomaly review\n\n🛠 ops\n  incident summarization + postmortems\n\n💡 founder\n  strategy sparring + market research\n\n💻 eng\n  code review + design-doc sparring\n\n📣 marketing\n  copy variants + image generation\n\n⚖️ legal\n  contract review + clause flagging",
